Introduce on demand Goro implementation

title: Introduce on demand Goro implementation
message:
Introduce on demand Goro implementation

The implementation tries to bind to the worker service when one of Goro methods is invoked.
Then it passes all the tasks to Goro instance behind the service and unbinds.

Closes #4.

title: Change BoundGoro implementation
message:
Change BoundGoro implementation

bindOneshot() is removed from BoundGoro interface.
When BoundGoro is created, unexpected service disconnection strategy must be
defined explicitly.

Version is set to 3.0.
